Teacher Assistant

CYB1003 - Introduction to Cybersecurity

Summer 2024

I've been offered to take charge of 2 groups of first year students in Computer Science, at the Université du Québec en Outaouais. Under the supervision of Myria Bouhaddi Ph.D, I was in charge of the lab sessions, where I was able to help the students with the following subjects :



  • Affine Cryptography
  • Substitution Cryptography
  • Polybe Square Cryptography
  • Permutation Cryptography
  • Vigenere Crypto
  • Vernam
  • Hill
  • RSA
  • Feistel
  • DES
  • TCP/IP
  • Security Standards
  • IDS/IPS
  • Firewall ipTables
  • Risk Analysis
  • Access Control
  • VPN
  • Security Incident Investigation
